                                        class=""></path></svg
                                >
                                <span class="ms-6 grow"
                                    ><span
                                        class="block text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200"
                                        >Gain access to Cloud based MicroANPR. </span
                                    ><span
                                        class="mt-1 block text-neutral-800 hs-tab-active:text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hs-tab-active:text-neutral-200"
                                        >
                                        You donâ€™t need to purchase, install, update,  maintain, any hardware, or software. 
                                        </span
                                    ></will ensure the availability and the security of the app and your data as well. SaaS allows your organization to get quickly up and running with an app at minimal upfront cost.span
                                ></span
                            ></button
                        ><button
                            type="button"
                            class="rounded-xl p-4 text-start outline-none ring-zinc-500 transition duration-300 hover:bg-neutral-200 focus-visible:ring hs-tab-active:bg-neutral-50 hs-tab-active:shadow-md hs-tab-active:hover:border-transparent dark:ring-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-neutral-700 dark:focus:outline-none dark:hs-tab-active:bg-neutral-700/60 md:p-5"
                            id="tabs-with-card-item-2"
                            data-hs-tab="#tabs-with-card-2"
                            aria-controls="tabs-with-card-2"
                            role="tab"
                            ><span class="flex"
                                ><svg
                                    class="mt-2 h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 fill-neutral-700 hs-tab-active:fill-[#fa5a15] dark:fill-neutral-300 dark:hs-tab-active:fill-[#fb713b] md:h-7 md:w-7"
                                    height="48"
                                    viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                                    width="48"
                                    ><title></title><path
                                        d="M510-570v-270h330v270H510ZM120-450v-390h330v390H120Zm390 330v-390h330v390H510Zm-390 0v-270h330v270H120Zm60-390h210v-270H180v270Zm390 330h210v-270H570v270Zm0-450h210v-150H570v150ZM180-180h210v-150H180v150Zm210-330Zm180-120Zm0 180ZM390-330Z"
                                        class=""></path></svg
                                >
                                <span class="ms-6 grow"
                                    ><span
                                        class="block text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800  dark:text-neutral-200 ]"
                                        >Intuitive Dashboards</span
                                    ><span
                                        class="mt-1 block text-neutral-800 hs-tab-active:text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hs-tab-active:text-neutral-200"
                                        >
                                        Navigate with ease using intuitive dashboards. 
                                        </span
                                    ></span
                                ></span
                            ></button
                        ><button
                            type="button"
                            class="rounded-xl p-4 text-start outline-none ring-zinc-500 transition duration-300 hover:bg-neutral-200 focus-visible:ring hs-tab-active:bg-neutral-50 hs-tab-active:shadow-md hs-tab-active:hover:border-transparent dark:ring-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-neutral-700 dark:focus:outline-none dark:hs-tab-active:bg-neutral-700/60 md:p-5"
                            id="tabs-with-card-item-3"
                            data-hs-tab="#tabs-with-card-3"
                            aria-controls="tabs-with-card-3"
                            role="tab"
                            ><span class="flex"
                                ><svg
                                    class="h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-neutral-700 hs-tab-active:text-[#fa5a15] dark:text-neutral-300 dark:hs-tab-active:text-[#fb713b] md:h-7 md:w-7"
                                    height="24"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    width="24"
                                    fill="none"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    stroke-width="1.5"
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    ><title></title><path
                                        d="M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205 3 1m1.5.5-1.5-.5M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636 10.5-3.819"
