                                    ><span
                                        class="block text-lg font-bold text-neutral-800 hs-tab-active:text-[#fa5a15] dark:text-neutral-200 dark:hs-tab-active:text-[#fb713b]"
                                        >Robust Features</span
                                    ><span
                                        class="mt-1 block text-neutral-800 hs-tab-active:text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hs-tab-active:text-neutral-200"
                                        >Minimize complexity, maximize
                                        productivity and excellence.
                                        </span
                                    ></span
                                ></span
